      <h2>What Is a Nikah Nama?</h2>
      <p>The Nikah Nama is your Islamic marriage contract. In Pakistan, it serves as the legal and religious record of your marriage. It's issued by the Nikah Registrar at your local Union Council after the marriage ceremony.</p>

      <p>The document is legally binding under Pakistani law. It contains essential details that UAE authorities verify when processing visa and banking applications.</p>

